message.body: I got an email from the lady I emailed from jefferson, she said they're going to be reviewing my application within the next few weeks. O_O
Fingers crossed!
Mmmmhm! Pullin for ya, baby! You got this. Bout time they get to reviewing your app ha
I know. I hope so. But how have you been? We're going to eat pho right now. I miss you. I thought about you last night and I had a dream about you :D
Mm enjoy :) Im good. Getting outta bed now. Thinking about you all the time, my love, which makes everything better. Hope your dream was really good :)
It was. So good! Olive you baby!
*i love you
:-D i love you too!!!!
Did you get to work? You didn't call me :(
Im so sorry, darling! I was so sleepy, such a bad mood, barely made it to work. Sorry, my love. Wish i called. I really miss you. How was dinner?
It was good. No worries baby! I love you so much! Don't be in a bad mood anymore! I miS you too. I wish I were with you!
Good good :) And, is ok now. Accept my fate tonight haha. Would much prefer crawling into bed next to you.
Oh I completely agree. Valentine's Day can't come any sooner!
Oi, goodness cant wait!!!
Whatcha still doing awake, pretty lady?
Hehe. I was watching dr. Who. I'm going to bed now!!!! I love you soooooooooooo much.
Call me tomorrow!!!
Ahah that crazy show?! Silly lady. Love you with all my heart, darling. I will call you. See the faces on skype yea yea? Im skip a party to talk to ya mmhm :)
Oh baby. Don't skip anything for me!!! But I will Skype with you!
Haha i dont feel like getting up early to go to this particular gathering. Ppl from school speaking russian to each other on purpose for practice. Not my thing.
Soooo skype with my darling!
Oh I see. Yay! Hahah. Okie. Talk to you tomorrow then! I love you. Goodnight. Be safe getting home.
Night beauty :) Love you so much. Kiss you
Mmmm. 6-8 inches on snow Monday into Tuesday. Probably no class and no lab. That's so nice.
O nice! You get a play day! Wonder if we get any..even tho no class anyway. But great for my darling! Who isnt letting me sleep cause shes phooing me in my head
O_O I had a dream like that yesterday! We were on a bed, but it was in a middle of a living room. But we had to stop because someone came downstairs.
Ahaha well i cant sleep!! Might as well come over! No one will interrupt haha. Where on earth we were haha?? What bed is in the middle of a living room??
I have no idea. Hahahahaha. I think it was some party.
Ahahaha waahhh?? You crazy woman!
We did it!!!! Or at least tried to!!
Hahaha i hope we took each other home and typhooned each other. Cant do it at a party crazy haha. Too risky!
We did not. Because it turned into another dream. I guess we'll have to do that come Valentine's Day.
Ahhh well you go fix that pretty lady. Next time you dreamin, give us the whole place to ourselves :-p And V-day mmhmm. You done. Dont even bring clothes.

Hahahaha. You're silly. I love you!
I guess that's what Valentine's Day is all about, huh?
Haha love you lotta lot! (Just bring bus clothes). And naaaw, its about cards, and heart candies, charlie brown cartoons, etc :-p Maybe flowers and chocolate
Am I going to get all that????
Haha that work? What else ya want? Ive got a list

You've got a list of what? Flowers and cAndy? Haha
Grapes :)
Haha i'll keep mental note of everything you want for that weekend ha. Hit me with it ha
I think that's good for now.
JENNY BREAKFAST!
Ahah of coooourse! Thats a given!!
Imma try to fall asleep now...buuut what time can i see yo face?!
Whenever you wake up! Or whenever you want.
Mmm imma try to get up at 3...as pooey as that is. I call ya. Love you!! Have a wonderful day til then, darling!
You too!! Goodnight baby
Night my love :)
You still sleeping?
